title: The 5 Dollar Phone Is REAL
description:
The Viva V1 is the cheapest phone I've ever featured on Unbox Therapy. It's made in India and for that market but has interesting implications for the tech world as a whole. It's not the 4 dollar smartphone that was promised but it's cool nonetheless.
